The paper discusses state management in big data processing systems, which involves handling and implementing state for complex operations in various applications. This topic is closely related to data structures (cs.DS), databases (cs.DB), distributed computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), and systems and control (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
